[I] Certificate manager and GUI for OpenPGP and CMS cryptography

[T] Kleopatra is an open-source certificate manager and graphical front-end for
[T] cryptographic services, primarily designed to handle OpenPGP and S/MIME
[T] (X.509) certificates.

[U] https://apps.kde.org/kleopatra/

